Package org.shared.net.handler

A package of ConnectionHandler implementations.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    FilteredHandler<H extends FilteredHandler<H,C,T>,C extends Connection,T>
    Defines a ConnectionHandler that uses Filters to process inbound and outbound data.
    OobHandler<C extends Connection>
    Defines a ConnectionHandler that can react to user-defined OobEvents.
    SynchronousHandler.Resolver
    Defines a gadget that supports SynchronousHandler.ManagedInputStream and SynchronousHandler.ManagedOutputStream.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractFilteredHandler<H extends AbstractFilteredHandler<H,C,T>,C extends Connection,T>
    An abstract base class implementing much of FilteredHandler.
    SynchronousHandler<C extends Connection>
    A subclass of AbstractFilteredHandler with synchronous behavior.
    XmlHandler<H extends XmlHandler<H,C,T,S>,C extends Connection,T extends XmlEvent<T,?,S>,S extends Enum<S>>
    A null-terminated packet protocol for reading and writing XmlEvents.
